{"tha-ap50:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap50:0.2":"Upalivagga ","tha-ap50:0.3":"8 Cankamanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap50:1.1":"“Atthadassissa munino, ","tha-ap50:1.2":"lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap50:1.3":"Itthakahi cinitvana, ","tha-ap50:1.4":"cankamam karayim aham. ","tha-ap50:2.1":"Uccato pancaratanam, ","tha-ap50:2.2":"cankamam sadhumapitam; ","tha-ap50:2.3":"Ayamato hatthasatam, ","tha-ap50:2.4":"bhavaniyyam manoramam. ","tha-ap50:3.1":"Patiggahesi bhagava, ","tha-ap50:3.2":"atthadassi naruttamo; ","tha-ap50:3.3":"Hatthena pulinam gayha, ","tha-ap50:3.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap50:4.1":"‘Imina pulinadanena, ","tha-ap50:4.2":"cankamam sukatena ca; ","tha-ap50:4.3":"Sattaratanasampannam, ","tha-ap50:4.4":"pulinam anubhossati. ","tha-ap50:5.1":"Tini kappani devesu, ","tha-ap50:5.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap50:5.3":"Anubhossati sampattim, ","tha-ap50:5.4":"accharahi purakkhato. ","tha-ap50:6.1":"Manussalokamagantva, ","tha-ap50:6.2":"raja ratthe bhavissati; ","tha-ap50:6.3":"Tikkhattum cakkavatti ca, ","tha-ap50:6.4":"mahiya so bhavissati’. ","tha-ap50:7.1":"Attharase kappasate, ","tha-ap50:7.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap50:7.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap50:7.4":"cankamassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap50:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap50:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap50:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap50:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma cankamanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap50:10.1":"Cankamanadayakattherassapadanam atthamam. "}